  "subject": "AAI-1468 Add connectivity schema for CCVPN usecase",
  "commit_message": "AAI-1468 Add connectivity schema for CCVPN usecase\n\nIssue-ID: AAI-1468\nAdd connectivities sub-component to \"network\" namespace.\nAdd connectivities element, which is sequence of \"connectivity\".\nAdd connectivity element, which has numerous properties.\nMake the following properties indexed and searchable:\nconnectivity-id, etht-svc-name, operational-status\n\nChange-Id: I29660beb357381612ff239ae2304c97dcd4532f0\nSigned-off-by: Keong Lim <keong.lim@huawei.com>\n",
